  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe made it to 2016.\u0026nbsp; Laser researchers have published some ground breaking papers.\u0026nbsp; Sports teams that are using Super Pulsed Laser are dominating the playing field.\u0026nbsp; 2015 was a good year, and 2016 will be even better.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003ESo, as has been tradition it\u0026rsquo;s time to kick off our new year Webinar schedule with a Review of some important laser principles basics, clinical guidelines and protocol development tools.\u0026nbsp; Join Dr. Christopher Carraway to start up right with Laser. \u0026nbsp;Keeping abreast of laser basics will put you on solid ground moving forward to more advanced work and better outcomes.\u0026nbsp; So let\u0026rsquo;s get started Right with the Light.\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
